    <!-- Notation stave over a 6-line TAB stave, 4/4: the same ascending line on string 1
         duplicated as voice 1 (pitched, staff 1) and voice 2 (fretted, staff 2). Only the
         note durations vary per measure, so the dotted rhythms render on both staves with
         the tab frets staying aligned under their noteheads. divisions=4. -->
